        public static boolean isImage(java.lang.String imagePath)
        Check is filepath corresponds to a readable compatible image file. (The implementation is still incomplete, the file contents is not inspected for a valid image.).

        requires: imagePath != null && !imagePath.isEmpty()

        Parameters:
        imagePath - image's file path
        Returns:
        boolean true if is a valid image file, otherwise it returns false
